txt.en: There are bears dwelling in Nan Tornaeth, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Nan Tornaeth, you should put down the maddened bears which dwell there, ending their suffering.
The maddened bears of Nan Tornaeth are beyond hope, thanks to the wights which have risen in the hills.
